```
2026-01-02 10:21:05 [WARNING] scylla.e2e.llm_judge: LLM judge failed, using fallback: [Errno 7] Argument list too long: 'claude'
```

### T6 Success (after fix)
```
T6: PASS (score: 0.700, cost: $0.4037)
Frontier CoP: $0.4037
```

